column5: I am looking to see if anyone knows if there are any drive to camps with a husband/wife specials for either Sunset Country or North of superior. We are looking for a cabin/boat package for mid to late July.We are looking for a modern cabin with a variety of fish species. Thanks
O'Sullivan's Rainbow on O'Sullivan Lake has a chart showing availability on their website. Good fishing, heading up there in July. www.osullivansrainbow.com Bill
